  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Driving after Brexit for UK licence holders living in the EU
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Check if you need to exchange your UK driving licence or get your vehicle retested after Brexit, if you live in the EU.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

